UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 536
1 A RESOLUTION confirming the appointment of Amy Miller to the Board of Tax
2 Appeals.
3 WHEREAS, on May 21, 2025, in accordance with KRS 49.020 and by virtue of
4 Executive Order 2025-309, Governor Andy Beshear appointed Amy Miller to the Board
5 of Tax Appeals for a term expiring June 29, 2029; and
6 WHEREAS, the appointment is subject to Senate confirmation; and
7 WHEREAS, Amy Miller has been determined to meet the requirements of KRS
8 49.020;
9 NOW, THEREFORE,
10 Be it resolved by the Senate of the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of
11 Kentucky:
12 Section 1. The Senate hereby confirms the appointment of Amy Miller to the
13 Board of Tax Appeals.
14 Section 2. The Clerk of the Senate shall forward a copy of this Resolution and
15 notification of its adoption to Amy Miller of Harlan, Harlan County, Kentucky, and to
16 Governor Andy Beshear, 703 Capital Avenue, Room 133, Frankfort, Kentucky 40601.
